messages.message: Have we thought about offering the option to duplicate projects in Build? Would be helpful if multiple folks want to iterate on a project, and also just easier to compare which project version performs better over larger sample sizes
I've also found myself wishing for the ability to duplicate projects. Or maybe just version them? Not sure which is preferable.
duplicating projects would make the cypress tests less flaky and run faster, if it meant not having to redigitize everything...
